 are turned loose against me;"},{"kind":"text","text":" they chase my dignity away like the wind,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and my prosperity has passed by like a cloud."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 18:11","book":"Job","chapter":18,"verse":11},{"label":"Jb 27:20","book":"Job","chapter":27,"verse":20},{"label":"Ps 73:19","book":"Psa","chapter":73,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:30:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now my life is poured out before me,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and days of suffering "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 10:15","book":"Job","chapter":10,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 30:27","book":"Job","chapter":30,"verse":27,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 36:21","book":"Job","chapter":36,"verse":21,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" have seized me."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 10:15","book":"Job","chapter":10,"verse":15},{"label":"Jb 30:27","book":"Job","chapter":30,"verse":27},{"label":"Jb 36:21","book":"Job","chapter":36,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:30:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Night pierces my bones,"},{"kind":"text","text":" but my gnawing pains never rest. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 33:19","book":"Job","chapter":33,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 6:2","book":"Psa","chapter":6,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 38:3","book":"Psa","chapter":38,"verse":3,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 33:19","book":"Job","chapter":33,"verse":19},{"label":"Ps 6:2","book":"Psa","chapter":6,"verse":2},{"label":"Ps 38:3","book":"Psa","chapter":38,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:30:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"My clothing is distorted with great force;"},{"kind":"text","text":" he chokes me by the neck of my garment. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Hb obscure"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Hb obscure"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:30:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He throws me into the mud,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and I have become like dust and ashes. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 16:15","book":"Job","chapter":16,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 7:5","book":"Psa","chapter":7,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 75:10","book":"Psa","chapter":75,"verse":10,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 16:15","book":"Job","chapter":16,"verse":15},{"label":"Ps 7:5","book":"Psa","chapter":7,"verse":5},{"label":"Ps 75:10","book":"Psa","chapter":75,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:30:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I cry out to you for help, but you do not answer me; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 19:7","book":"Job","chapter":19,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 18:41","book":"Psa","chapter":18,"verse":41,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 88:13–14","book":"Psa","chapter":88,"verse":13,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" when I stand up, you merely look at me."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 19:7","book":"Job","chapter":19,"verse":7},{"label":"Ps 18:41","book":"Psa","chapter":18,"verse":41},{"label":"Ps 88:13–14","book":"Psa","chapter":88,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:30:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You have turned against me with cruelty;"},{"kind":"text","text":" you harass "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 49:23","book":"Gen","chapter":49,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 16:9","book":"Job","chapter":16,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 55:3","book":"Psa","chapter":55,"verse":3,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" me with your strong hand."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 49:23","book":"Gen","chapter":49,"verse":23},{"label":"Jb 16:9","book":"Job","chapter":16,"verse":9},{"label":"Ps 55:3","book":"Psa","chapter":55,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:30:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You lift me up on the wind and make me ride it;"},{"kind":"text","text":" you scatter me in the storm. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 9:17","book":"Job","chapter":9,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 83:15","book":"Psa","chapter":83,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jnh 1:4","book":"Jon","chapter":1,"verse":4,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 9:17","book":"Job","chapter":9,"verse":17},{"label":"Ps 83:15","book":"Psa","chapter":83,"verse":15},{"label":"Jnh 1:4","book":"Jon","chapter":1,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:30:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Yes, I know that you will lead me to death —"},{"kind":"text","text":" the place "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 3:15","book":"Job","chapter":3,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 17:13","book":"Job","chapter":17,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ec 12:5","book":"Ecc","chapter":12,"verse":5,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" appointed for all who live."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 3:15","book":"Job","chapter":3,"verse":15},{"label":"Jb 17:13","book":"Job","chapter":17,"verse":13},{"label":"Ec 12:5","book":"Ecc","chapter":12,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:30:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Yet no one would stretch out his hand"},{"kind":"text","text":" against a ruined person "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit a heap of ruins"},{"kind":"text","text":" when he cries out to him for help"},{"kind":"text","text":" because of his distress. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 12:5","book":"Job","chapter":12,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 31:29","book":"Job","chapter":31,"verse":29,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 24:22","book":"Pro","chapter":24,"verse":22,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 12:5","book":"Job","chapter":12,"verse":5},{"label":"Jb 31:29","book":"Job","chapter":31,"verse"